# Dev Server

- The dev server runs on `http://localhost:3000`. NEVER start a new instance.
- If port 3000 is not responding, ask the user to restart the server — do NOT launch `pnpm dev` yourself.
- NEVER use alternative ports (3001, 3002, etc.). Only access the app on port 3000.
